verses.verse: And the <S%H1486>lot<s%> of the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H3130>Joseph<s%> <S%H3318>fell<s%> from <S%H3383>Jordan<s%> by <S%H3405>Jericho,<s%> to the <S%H4325>water<s%> of <S%H3405>Jericho<s%> on the <S%H4217>east,<s%> to the <S%H4057>wilderness<s%> that <S%H5927>goes<s%> up from <S%H3405>Jericho<s%> throughout <S%H2022>mount<s%> <S%H1008>Bethel,<s%>
And <S%H3318>goes<s%> out from <S%H1008>Bethel<s%> to <S%H3870>Luz,<s%> and <S%H5674>passes<s%> along to the <S%H1366>borders<s%> of <S%H757>Archi<s%> to <S%H5852>Ataroth,<s%>

And <S%H3381>goes<s%> <S%H3381>down<s%> <S%H3220>westward<s%> to the <S%H1366>coast<s%> of <S%H3311>Japhleti,<s%> to the <S%H1366>coast<s%> of <S%H1032>Bethhoron<s%> the <S%H8481>nether,<s%> and to <S%H1507>Gezer;<s%> and the <S%H8444>goings<s%> out thereof are at the <S%H3220>sea.<s%>
So the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H3130>Joseph,<s%> <S%H4519>Manasseh<s%> and <S%H669>Ephraim,<s%> took their <S%H5157>inheritance.<s%>

And the <S%H1366>border<s%> of the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H669>Ephraim<s%> according to their <S%H4940>families<s%> was thus: even the <S%H1366>border<s%> of their <S%H5159>inheritance<s%> on the <S%H4217>east<s%> side was <S%H5853>Atarothaddar,<s%> to <S%H1032>Bethhoron<s%> the <S%H5945>upper;<s%>

And the <S%H1366>border<s%> <S%H3318>went<s%> out toward the <S%H3220>sea<s%> to <S%H4366>Michmethah<s%> on the <S%H6828>north<s%> side; and the <S%H1366>border<s%> <S%H5437>went<s%> <S%H5437>about<s%> <S%H4217>eastward<s%> to <S%H8387>Taanathshiloh,<s%> and <S%H5674>passed<s%> by it on the <S%H4217>east<s%> to <S%H3239>Janohah;<s%>

And it <S%H3381>went<s%> <S%H3381>down<s%> from <S%H3239>Janohah<s%> to <S%H5852>Ataroth,<s%> and to <S%H5292>Naarath,<s%> and <S%H6293>came<s%> to <S%H3405>Jericho,<s%> and <S%H3318>went<s%> out at <S%H3383>Jordan.<s%>

The <S%H1366>border<s%> <S%H3212>went<s%> out from <S%H8599>Tappuah<s%> <S%H3220>westward<s%> to the <S%H5158>river<s%> <S%H7071>Kanah;<s%> and the <S%H8444>goings<s%> out thereof were at the <S%H3220>sea.<s%> <S%H2063>This<s%> is the <S%H5159>inheritance<s%> of the <S%H4294>tribe<s%> of the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H669>Ephraim<s%> by their <S%H4940>families.<s%>

And the <S%H3995>separate<s%> <S%H5892>cities<s%> for the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H669>Ephraim<s%> were <S%H8432>among<s%> the <S%H5159>inheritance<s%> of the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H4519>Manasseh,<s%> <S%H3605>all<s%> the <S%H5892>cities<s%> with their <S%H2691>villages.<s%>

And they <S%H3423>drove<s%> not out the <S%H3669>Canaanites<s%> that <S%H3427>dwelled<s%> in <S%H1507>Gezer:<s%> but the <S%H3669>Canaanites<s%> <S%H3427>dwell<s%> <S%H7130>among<s%> the <S%H669>Ephraimites<s%> to <S%H2088>this<s%> <S%H3117>day,<s%> and <S%H5647>serve<s%> under <S%H4522>tribute.<s%>
